WEBVTT

01:37.140 --> 01:40.990
[The Best Thing]

01:41.420 --> 01:48.520
[Episode 24]
[Albizia Bark]
[Sweet in taste, neutral in nature, relieves depression, calms the mind, promotes blood circulation, and reduces swelling.]

02:24.310 --> 02:25.420
Hello, Ms. Liu.

02:25.420 --> 02:26.660
I forgot the key.

02:26.660 --> 02:28.540
Where did you put our spare key?

02:29.070 --> 02:29.790
The spare key

02:29.790 --> 02:31.440
is at Ms. Zhao's place in Unit 4.

02:31.910 --> 02:33.700
But they went on a trip, so there's no one home.

02:34.980 --> 02:36.140
Alright, never mind then.

02:36.140 --> 02:37.100
I'll ask Xiangya.

02:37.100 --> 02:38.660
I have a spare key with her.

02:38.660 --> 02:39.870
I'll have her send it to me via flash delivery.

02:40.329 --> 02:42.490
Okay, let me know once you get in.

02:42.750 --> 02:43.350
Alright.

02:43.350 --> 02:43.980
Bye.

02:44.220 --> 02:44.860
Bye.

02:53.150 --> 02:53.950
Xiangya,

02:53.980 --> 02:55.370
can you send me a key via flash delivery?

02:55.390 --> 02:56.579
I'll give you an address.

02:56.700 --> 02:57.420
Hurry up,

02:57.420 --> 02:58.470
or I won't be able to get home.

03:13.420 --> 03:14.750
I just got out of the shower.

03:14.750 --> 03:16.140
Where are you? I'll send it over.

03:18.470 --> 03:19.820
I'm at He Suye's place.

03:25.480 --> 03:27.930
Then why not just stay at his place?

03:28.370 --> 03:29.460
I'm going to sleep now. Goodnight.

03:58.310 --> 03:59.260
What did Xiangya say?

04:01.860 --> 04:04.260
She said she happens to be out,

04:04.260 --> 04:05.040
so...

04:05.150 --> 04:07.340
she can't send me the key.

04:16.310 --> 04:17.800
So, you...

04:18.250 --> 04:19.649
can't go home tonight?

04:23.190 --> 04:23.800
Right.

04:25.000 --> 04:26.080
So...

04:26.190 --> 04:27.310
I might have to...

04:28.220 --> 04:30.110
stay at your place for the night.

04:38.630 --> 04:40.070
I only have one bedroom.

04:45.050 --> 04:46.460
How about I sleep on the couch?

04:48.700 --> 04:50.990
Wouldn't it be inappropriate to make you sleep on the couch because of me?

04:51.340 --> 04:53.190
And it's not very comfortable.

04:53.190 --> 04:54.550
Yeah. Indeed.

05:18.550 --> 05:19.430
Later...

05:19.950 --> 05:21.870
can you lend me a pair of pajamas

05:21.870 --> 05:23.790
and a bath towel?

05:23.950 --> 05:25.710
I want to take a shower first.

05:29.870 --> 05:30.990
A shower first, huh?

05:31.950 --> 05:32.340
Alright.

05:32.340 --> 05:33.900
I'll go get a towel.

05:34.510 --> 05:35.140
Wait.

05:37.190 --> 05:40.110
I don't have pajamas in your size.

05:41.030 --> 05:42.990
How about you wear my clothes?

05:44.850 --> 05:46.720
Well, thanks.

05:47.650 --> 05:48.930
Okay, I'll go get them.

06:10.020 --> 06:10.870
He Suye,

06:11.220 --> 06:13.270
where's the hairdryer?

06:14.140 --> 06:16.220
It's in the drawer under the sink.

06:55.820 --> 06:56.750
What's wrong?

06:57.670 --> 06:58.630
I'm...

06:58.630 --> 06:59.460
just looking at you.

07:29.750 --> 07:30.430
If you keep doing this,

07:30.430 --> 07:31.700
I won't be able to dry my hair.

07:32.120 --> 07:33.150
I'll do it for you.

07:47.630 --> 07:50.810
♫Never know what to do♫

07:50.990 --> 07:54.300
♫In the times, I'm with you♫

07:58.280 --> 08:01.320
♫Never know what to say♫

08:01.600 --> 08:05.700
♫In the hours, I'm with you♫

08:08.990 --> 08:12.260
♫All I know, that it's true♫

08:14.620 --> 08:18.370
♫That it's true♫

08:19.660 --> 08:22.480
♫That I find myself♫

08:23.110 --> 08:26.460
♫Drawn to you♫

08:30.260 --> 08:33.460
♫In the window shades♫

08:33.809 --> 08:38.880
♫Look at the colors we made♫

08:40.650 --> 08:44.380
♫I am not afraid♫

08:44.650 --> 08:51.380
♫We're gonna find a way♫

09:15.800 --> 09:19.080
♫All I know, that it's true♫

09:21.220 --> 09:24.840
♫It's always been true♫

09:26.310 --> 09:29.510
♫That I find myself♫

09:29.910 --> 09:33.340
♫Drawn to you♫

09:36.580 --> 09:40.090
♫In the window shades♫

09:40.620 --> 09:46.090
♫Look at the colors we made♫

09:47.640 --> 09:50.840
♫I am not afraid♫

09:51.300 --> 09:57.340
♫We're gonna find a way♫

10:22.030 --> 10:22.990
Sleep a little longer.

10:24.740 --> 10:25.340
Okay.

10:38.860 --> 10:39.670
What are you doing?

10:41.310 --> 10:44.310
You like the smell of your shampoo so much?

10:48.100 --> 10:49.700
Is this the smell of my shampoo?

10:51.530 --> 10:54.290
Didn't I take a shower at your place yesterday?

10:55.580 --> 10:57.910
Why does it not smell like that to me?

11:06.160 --> 11:06.590
Alright.

11:06.620 --> 11:07.550
Get up and wash up.

11:08.800 --> 11:11.040
No, I haven't slept enough yet.

11:14.620 --> 11:15.790
You didn't

11:16.430 --> 11:17.870
have enough sleep last night?

11:48.060 --> 11:49.510
He Suye!

11:49.530 --> 11:50.960
Go wash up. Go!

11:51.690 --> 11:52.330
Out!

11:52.980 --> 11:54.070
Then I'll go wash up first.

12:10.240 --> 12:11.830
Are you awake?

12:11.860 --> 12:13.500
Do you still need me to send the key?

12:19.180 --> 12:20.420
No need.

12:51.310 --> 12:52.270
What do you want to do this afternoon?

12:54.490 --> 12:55.590
This afternoon?

12:56.080 --> 12:56.830
What do you want to do?

12:57.250 --> 12:58.250
You're asking me?

13:00.390 --> 13:01.460
Well...

13:01.460 --> 13:02.190
let's go shopping

13:02.580 --> 13:03.690
and buy some daily necessities.

13:03.880 --> 13:04.760
And...

13:04.790 --> 13:05.820
let's buy two sets of pajamas.

13:06.670 --> 13:07.610
Buy pajamas?

13:10.070 --> 13:12.440
If you still want to wear my clothes,

13:12.550 --> 13:13.390
I don't mind.

13:15.570 --> 13:16.200
Just go.

13:18.150 --> 13:18.670
Alright.

13:18.720 --> 13:19.690
You wash up now.

13:19.710 --> 13:20.700
I'll go make something to eat.

13:34.160 --> 13:35.140
Pajamas...

13:55.510 --> 13:56.510
He Suye,

13:56.800 --> 13:59.110
can you come with me to buy shampoo and conditioner?

14:00.580 --> 14:01.400
What's wrong?

14:01.700 --> 14:03.430
You don't like the smell of my shampoo?

14:04.390 --> 14:05.280
It's just that...

14:05.430 --> 14:06.430
it doesn't suit me.

14:09.070 --> 14:11.270
I think that scent suits you well.

14:12.140 --> 14:12.980
Come on.

14:32.710 --> 14:33.990
Lemon-scented?

14:50.900 --> 14:52.110
Which one do you think I should buy?

14:52.130 --> 14:53.920
One citrus-scented and one lemon-scented.

14:56.780 --> 14:58.210
Citrus-scented and lemon-scented?

15:00.470 --> 15:01.440
Just buy both.

15:02.480 --> 15:03.200
Both?

15:04.060 --> 15:04.910
Use them alternately.

15:05.120 --> 15:06.380
You will often come to my place

15:06.670 --> 15:07.700
to use them anyway.

15:10.940 --> 15:11.580
Let's go and pay.

15:12.190 --> 15:14.190
Who's going to come and use them often?

15:14.910 --> 15:16.480
I'll take these three basic ones.

15:16.500 --> 15:17.050
Okay.

15:17.430 --> 15:18.670
Do you only use these usually?

15:19.190 --> 15:21.170
No. But the full set isn't on sale.

15:21.200 --> 15:22.550
I'll just get the basic ones.

15:22.910 --> 15:23.550
It's alright.

15:23.800 --> 15:25.090
We'll take two of this set.

15:25.690 --> 15:26.260
Okay.

15:26.790 --> 15:27.700
Two sets?

15:28.280 --> 15:29.250
Why?

15:30.000 --> 15:31.290
Didn't I just say?

15:31.320 --> 15:33.360
You can come and use them often at my place.

15:35.270 --> 15:35.820
No, wait.

15:36.220 --> 15:37.340
Two sets won't be enough. Make it three.

15:37.680 --> 15:38.600
Okay, please wait a moment.

15:39.950 --> 15:42.060
Three sets? You're being too exaggerated.

15:42.100 --> 15:42.740
Don't worry.

15:42.740 --> 15:43.550
You'll use them up.

15:46.990 --> 15:49.540
Now that we've finished buying skincare products,

15:49.560 --> 15:51.490
what do you think we should buy next?

15:57.120 --> 15:57.960
Pajamas.

16:07.070 --> 16:08.950
Is this the kind of pajamas you wear?

16:10.880 --> 16:11.570
Yeah.

16:13.290 --> 16:14.720
Look how cute it is.

16:16.690 --> 16:17.640
Let me tell you,

16:17.890 --> 16:20.150
the fabric in this store is super comfortable.

16:20.460 --> 16:22.460
How about I buy you a set too?

16:22.490 --> 16:24.060
We can wear matching ones at home.

16:29.130 --> 16:29.780
Alright.

16:58.980 --> 16:59.570
Coffee.

16:59.950 --> 17:00.980
Thank you.

17:01.970 --> 17:02.760
What are you looking at?

17:03.330 --> 17:04.720
Look at this flower.

17:04.750 --> 17:05.770
It's so beautiful.

17:05.790 --> 17:07.460
It's like a pink dandelion.

17:09.030 --> 17:09.900
It is quite beautiful.

17:10.420 --> 17:11.310
Isn't it?

17:32.660 --> 17:37.550
[Summer]

17:41.260 --> 17:42.060
Ms. Shen!

17:42.350 --> 17:43.270
Ms. Shen!

17:43.360 --> 17:44.030
He.

17:45.820 --> 17:46.740
Mr. and Mrs. Shen.

17:48.150 --> 17:50.830
You two went shopping with so many things?

17:51.160 --> 17:53.050
These are just some of our daily necessities.

17:53.950 --> 17:54.670
Stop standing here.

17:54.670 --> 17:55.260
Let's go home.

17:55.630 --> 17:57.020
I'll put these things at my place first.

17:57.230 --> 17:58.300
I'll come later.

18:03.290 --> 18:03.880
It's...

18:09.350 --> 18:11.420
I forgot my key last night,

18:11.450 --> 18:13.450
so I stayed at his place.

18:23.590 --> 18:24.190
Mrs. Shen,

18:25.090 --> 18:26.300
this is for you.

18:27.180 --> 18:28.070
Thank you.

18:35.020 --> 18:37.150
Well... tonight, come back...

18:39.660 --> 18:40.790
Come over for dinner.

18:43.360 --> 18:44.120
Come over.

18:46.880 --> 18:48.120
Okay, I'll... come over.

18:48.140 --> 18:48.970
He'll come on.

18:49.600 --> 18:50.800
Okay, then...

18:50.830 --> 18:51.980
Let's go home and cook.

18:51.980 --> 18:52.830
Let's go, let's go.

18:55.670 --> 18:56.670
What were you talking about?

18:56.700 --> 18:57.670
I didn't mean it.

19:03.070 --> 19:04.140
Let's go.

19:13.740 --> 19:15.260
This is my house.

19:15.980 --> 19:17.490
How did it turn into a password lock?

19:26.700 --> 19:27.670
You're back.

19:28.850 --> 19:30.530
This lock...

19:31.670 --> 19:32.460
The old one was broken.

19:32.460 --> 19:32.910
Yes.

19:33.260 --> 19:34.460
The key didn't work.

19:34.460 --> 19:36.540
We had no choice but to change it.

19:36.540 --> 19:37.630
From now on, we'll use the password.

19:38.020 --> 19:38.950
That way, you won't need

19:38.950 --> 19:40.220
a key to get in.

19:41.260 --> 19:42.370
The password is...

19:42.400 --> 19:43.680
It's Ms. Shen's birthday.

19:45.460 --> 19:46.220
Got it?

19:47.230 --> 19:47.960
Yes.

19:48.960 --> 19:50.200
Remember it for her.

19:50.540 --> 19:51.380
I got it.

19:51.720 --> 19:52.620
Give it a try.

19:57.270 --> 19:58.270
Well, I'll give it a try.

20:07.430 --> 20:08.590
The operation failed.

20:09.170 --> 20:10.870
It's wrong. Your dad set the wrong password.

20:35.640 --> 20:37.770
Why is he in such a good mood again?

21:04.610 --> 21:06.150
What are you two up to?

21:06.650 --> 21:07.970
Nothing.

21:08.550 --> 21:10.180
In case you forget your key in the future,

21:10.210 --> 21:12.120
I'm carrying the spare key with me.

21:13.090 --> 21:13.930
You can make another copy.

21:13.990 --> 21:14.940
I can keep one at my place.

21:17.600 --> 21:18.450
No need.

21:24.360 --> 21:25.680
What I mean is,

21:25.700 --> 21:28.110
we have already changed it to an electronic lock,

21:28.140 --> 21:30.060
so keys aren't necessary anymore.

21:33.680 --> 21:35.510
An electronic lock?

21:35.540 --> 21:38.300
So fancy.

21:42.720 --> 21:44.240
Have you finished your theses?

21:44.610 --> 21:45.430
Yes.

21:45.630 --> 21:46.350
Of course.

21:46.540 --> 21:47.780
Today is the deadline.

21:47.780 --> 21:48.900
What day is it today?

21:49.220 --> 21:50.430
You haven't finished your thesis yet?

21:51.120 --> 21:52.160
Don't you want to graduate?

21:52.190 --> 21:54.110
I'm almost done. I'm at the acknowledgments.

21:55.070 --> 21:55.700
Almost?

21:56.850 --> 21:57.920
Hurry up and finish it.

21:57.940 --> 21:59.410
That way, I can take a look at it for you when you're done.

22:01.920 --> 22:02.580
Oh, right.

22:02.680 --> 22:04.130
I'll be attending your thesis defense.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.540
The principal asked me to sit in.

22:06.190 --> 22:07.190
Why?

22:07.950 --> 22:09.490
Why do you have so many questions?

22:09.540 --> 22:10.660
Just hurry up and finish your thesis.

22:20.670 --> 22:21.360
That's enough.

22:21.790 --> 22:24.150
It's uncomfortable for a guy to apply so much.

22:24.150 --> 22:25.830
But every time, you make it so thick, like glue.

22:26.190 --> 22:29.060
Do you know aging happens in an instant?

22:29.060 --> 22:30.060
You're already 32.

22:30.060 --> 22:31.390
-You need to learn how to take good care of your skin.
-Wait.

22:31.390 --> 22:32.380
What's wrong with me being 32?

22:33.260 --> 22:35.260
My face still looks fine, right?

22:35.950 --> 22:37.430
At least I look younger than Song Feng.

22:37.740 --> 22:39.150
Why don't you compare yourself to Li Jie?

22:39.950 --> 22:41.370
What's there to compare between me and Li Jie?

22:56.420 --> 22:57.940
Are you seriously jealous of Li Jie?

22:59.780 --> 23:01.130
I won't be jealous anymore. Just apply it.

23:02.940 --> 23:04.670
Let me help you rub it in.

23:07.670 --> 23:08.390
Oh, right.

23:08.950 --> 23:10.300
In a couple of days, I'm going to attend

23:10.300 --> 23:11.910
the master's thesis defense.

23:11.910 --> 23:13.050
Can you help me put together an outfit?

23:13.910 --> 23:15.150
No problem, leave it to me.

23:15.250 --> 23:16.110
Make me look good.

23:16.260 --> 23:17.430
Don't worry.

23:30.020 --> 23:32.160
[Jiangzhou Traditional Chinese Medicine University]

24:07.820 --> 24:09.440
[Thesis Defense for 2021 Master's Degree Candidates]

24:10.150 --> 24:11.580
[Jiangzhou Traditional Chinese Medicine University]

24:26.500 --> 24:27.220
Hello,

24:27.220 --> 24:27.910
professors and experts.

24:27.910 --> 24:30.110
I'm Li Jie, a graduate student from the class of 2021.

24:30.460 --> 24:32.590
This is the topic of my graduation thesis.

24:34.540 --> 24:35.390
I will present my defense

24:35.390 --> 24:36.350
in five aspects:

24:36.350 --> 24:37.150
research background,

24:37.150 --> 24:38.110
research objectives,

24:38.110 --> 24:39.150
research content,

24:39.150 --> 24:40.910
research results,

24:40.910 --> 24:42.590
and the limitations and outlook of my thesis.

24:43.150 --> 24:45.460
Cervical cancer patients have severe symptoms,

24:45.460 --> 24:47.540
and their post-operative conditions vary widely.

26:44.910 --> 26:47.770
Finally, I'd like to thank my mentor, Professor Yu Liren,

26:47.800 --> 26:49.600
for his careful guidance over the past three years,

26:50.110 --> 26:51.670
and also Senior He Suye

26:51.670 --> 26:53.110
for his encouragement and help,

26:53.440 --> 26:55.440
as well as my friends and classmates for their company.

26:55.710 --> 26:56.520
Thank you, everyone.

27:09.390 --> 27:11.150
Thank you, Professor Yu.

27:12.440 --> 27:13.790
Through more than two years of hard work,

27:14.060 --> 27:16.150
you've proven your value.

27:16.480 --> 27:17.570
Professor Yu, this is because of your excellent guidance.

27:22.370 --> 27:23.240
Senior He.

27:24.910 --> 27:25.910
Your thesis is good.

27:26.260 --> 27:26.980
Congratulations

27:26.980 --> 27:27.950
on your successful graduation.

27:29.460 --> 27:31.430
Thank you for your encouragement and help before.

27:34.410 --> 27:35.580
I want to say that

27:36.060 --> 27:37.630
I've discussed it with the professor,

27:38.220 --> 27:39.150
and I might

27:39.150 --> 27:41.110
be transferred to the branch hospital in Ning City next week.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.360
So,

27:42.380 --> 27:43.540
I may be

27:43.590 --> 27:45.150
staying in Ning City from now on

27:45.760 --> 27:47.390
and might not have many chances to come back to Hang City.

27:55.170 --> 27:56.450
Grandpa told me that.

27:56.870 --> 27:58.700
The research center in Ning City

27:58.700 --> 27:59.890
actually has a lot of potential.

28:00.700 --> 28:01.500
I believe

28:01.500 --> 28:02.740
you will achieve great results soon.

28:04.300 --> 28:05.430
Thank you for your encouragement.

28:12.150 --> 28:13.430
I wish you success in your career

28:13.680 --> 28:14.810
and happiness in life.

28:16.740 --> 28:18.640
And I wish you a bright future.

28:46.840 --> 28:47.490
Go now.

29:06.370 --> 29:07.160
Fang Kexin.

29:09.430 --> 29:10.110
Li Jie?

29:10.430 --> 29:11.160
What's wrong?

29:12.910 --> 29:14.460
Didn't we agree

29:14.460 --> 29:15.820
to have dinner together after the defense?

29:16.950 --> 29:18.260
Yeah. Isn't it in the evening?

29:23.060 --> 29:23.830
What's wrong?

29:25.190 --> 29:26.500
Actually, I want to say...

29:35.500 --> 29:36.350
Fang Kexin,

29:36.780 --> 29:37.590
do you know

29:37.830 --> 29:38.780
that I like you?

30:06.960 --> 30:07.700
I'm sorry.

30:07.700 --> 30:08.350
Li Jie, I...

30:08.350 --> 30:09.630
We're good friends, right?

30:11.830 --> 30:12.590
Of course we are.

30:15.780 --> 30:16.590
Then I wish you

30:16.790 --> 30:17.870
success in your studies

30:17.950 --> 30:18.670
and a bright future.

30:21.180 --> 30:21.940
Bye.

30:48.150 --> 30:48.870
Professor,

30:49.590 --> 30:50.190
He,

30:51.220 --> 30:51.870
please stay.

30:52.850 --> 30:53.680
Principal.

30:54.590 --> 30:55.390
He,

30:55.980 --> 30:57.790
I specifically asked you to come today

30:57.810 --> 30:59.010
because I wanted to ask

30:59.110 --> 31:01.660
if you'd be interested in coming back to school to teach.

31:04.500 --> 31:06.430
You were an outstanding graduate,

31:06.660 --> 31:08.750
your performance during your PhD was excellent,

31:09.460 --> 31:11.260
and the four graduate students you mentored

31:11.260 --> 31:12.540
did very well under your guidance.

31:13.060 --> 31:13.780
So,

31:13.780 --> 31:15.890
the school held a meeting and discussed it.

31:16.040 --> 31:18.250
And we would like you to return and teach.

31:18.390 --> 31:20.630
You'll have four hours of elective courses each week

31:20.740 --> 31:22.450
and supervise internships at the hospital.

31:22.590 --> 31:24.120
That will be your teaching assignment.

31:24.870 --> 31:25.540
What do you think?

31:25.810 --> 31:26.720
Are you interested?

31:26.980 --> 31:27.950
Of course, I'm interested.

31:28.190 --> 31:29.070
Thank you, Principal.

31:29.300 --> 31:31.780
Thank you for giving him this opportunity,

31:32.380 --> 31:33.620
and thank the school

31:33.780 --> 31:34.810
for trusting him so much.

31:35.060 --> 31:35.980
I should thank you

31:35.980 --> 31:37.740
for having cultivated another talented TCM practitioner

31:37.740 --> 31:39.020
for the school and the country.

31:39.540 --> 31:40.540
On behalf of the school,

31:40.780 --> 31:41.540
I thank you.

31:41.780 --> 31:42.540
You're too kind.

32:12.260 --> 32:13.060
It's okay.

32:13.590 --> 32:14.500
You don't need to comfort me.

32:15.360 --> 32:16.950
I've already asked the question.

32:17.390 --> 32:18.500
That's already pretty good.

32:20.670 --> 32:22.110
I can finally give up hope.

32:23.350 --> 32:24.370
You've grown.

32:29.590 --> 32:30.300
I've grown.

32:33.150 --> 32:34.860
Well, since you've grown up,

32:35.000 --> 32:37.110
how about sending me the photos you just took?

32:39.290 --> 32:40.780
I need to send them to my girlfriend.

32:41.560 --> 32:43.110
She helped me put this outfit together.

32:43.130 --> 32:44.610
I should at least show her the result.

32:47.860 --> 32:50.450
Resisting you is also part of my growth.

32:51.700 --> 32:52.340
Li Jie,

32:53.550 --> 32:55.510
you'd better pray that during your PhD,

32:55.640 --> 32:56.920
you don't have to be my intern.

33:09.160 --> 33:09.840
Good boy.

33:10.590 --> 33:11.630
So ugly.

33:13.870 --> 33:14.390
Alright.

33:31.590 --> 33:32.190
Professor Yu!

33:33.220 --> 33:34.720
I'm here. I'm here.

33:35.110 --> 33:36.020
Mr. Shen?

33:36.460 --> 33:38.020
-What a coincidence.
-Yes.

33:38.020 --> 33:38.830
Such a coincidence.

33:38.830 --> 33:39.780
Did you go to buy vegetables?

33:39.780 --> 33:40.630
I bought some vegetables

33:40.630 --> 33:41.670
on my way home from work.

33:42.150 --> 33:43.020
Are you looking for He?

33:43.020 --> 33:44.910
Yeah. I finished the meeting early today.

33:45.190 --> 33:47.260
I want to ask him to join me for dinner.

33:47.260 --> 33:49.350
This kid, living alone, doesn't eat on time.

33:49.350 --> 33:50.300
He's always just making do.

33:50.830 --> 33:52.220
Hasn't he finished work yet?

33:52.850 --> 33:54.090
Why don't you come over to my place and have a seat?

33:54.180 --> 33:54.830
I won't be disturbing you, will I?

33:54.950 --> 33:55.980
Not at all.

33:55.980 --> 33:56.460
Okay.

33:56.830 --> 33:57.740
Sometimes,

33:57.740 --> 33:58.670
these two young people

33:58.670 --> 33:59.370
go out on dates

33:59.480 --> 34:00.500
after work,

34:00.520 --> 34:02.670
leaving just Ms. Liu and me at home.

34:03.650 --> 34:04.380
This way, this way.

34:04.430 --> 34:04.780
Okay.

34:04.780 --> 34:06.220
I'll call He later

34:06.220 --> 34:06.870
and tell him to come straight

34:06.890 --> 34:07.750
to our place after work.

34:10.750 --> 34:11.870
So silly.

34:12.070 --> 34:13.030
That's wonderful.

34:13.920 --> 34:17.120
Xifan was so beautiful at such a young age.

34:17.500 --> 34:18.580
Look at those eyes.

34:19.440 --> 34:20.510
You can tell by looking at her father

34:20.770 --> 34:22.530
that our family has good genes.

34:23.710 --> 34:24.620
Yes, yes.

34:26.659 --> 34:27.540
She was even wearing sunglasses.

34:27.540 --> 34:28.350
Such a little adult.

34:35.429 --> 34:36.460
Professor Yu,

34:36.460 --> 34:37.139
you're here.

34:37.139 --> 34:37.909
You're off work?

34:39.110 --> 34:40.679
Look who this is.

34:43.800 --> 34:44.719
Ms. Liu.

34:44.739 --> 34:46.139
He's been praising how cute you are.

34:46.139 --> 34:46.909
Hurry up and sit down.

34:46.909 --> 34:48.790
-Have a chat with Professor Yu.
-Put it away.

34:49.980 --> 34:50.580
Come on.

34:50.580 --> 34:51.310
Excuse me.

35:02.990 --> 35:03.580
This tea

35:03.580 --> 35:04.910
was also bought at a pharmacy.

35:04.910 --> 35:06.430
It's their prescription.

35:07.730 --> 35:09.170
You're showing off in front of an expert.

35:09.200 --> 35:10.110
Yes, yes.

35:10.710 --> 35:11.380
Not bad.

35:21.890 --> 35:22.850
Why are you laughing?

35:25.350 --> 35:26.580
Chef He.

35:31.690 --> 35:32.770
Where are your photos?

35:34.500 --> 35:35.310
Photos?

35:37.540 --> 35:38.350
What photos?

35:38.870 --> 35:40.150
Your childhood photos.

35:41.020 --> 35:42.140
Childhood?

35:42.790 --> 35:44.350
Why do you want to see my childhood photos?

35:44.350 --> 35:45.180
Those are all embarrassing memories.

35:45.180 --> 35:46.180
They're hideous. You're not allowed to see them.

35:46.580 --> 35:47.270
It's precisely because

35:47.270 --> 35:48.760
they're embarrassing that I want to see them.

35:48.950 --> 35:50.540
If they weren't, why would I want to see them?

35:52.910 --> 35:53.660
Why are you holding a bamboo shoot?

35:54.060 --> 35:54.980
Don't hit me. Don't make trouble.

35:54.980 --> 35:55.620
I'll beat you!

35:56.100 --> 35:56.910
Don't cause trouble.

35:57.430 --> 35:57.790
I'll bite you.

35:57.790 --> 35:58.230
Be gentle!

35:58.620 --> 35:59.230
You're trying to bite me, huh?

36:00.430 --> 36:01.580
Excuse me.

36:09.150 --> 36:13.070
If we don't cook now, it'll be too late to eat.

36:16.500 --> 36:17.710
I won't disturb you.

36:17.710 --> 36:18.790
No, no. You're not disturbing us.

36:18.790 --> 36:19.750
I'll get the drinks.

36:27.610 --> 36:28.440
I want to drink too.

36:33.020 --> 36:33.650
He.

36:33.800 --> 36:35.110
Let me help you.

36:35.140 --> 36:36.390
Otherwise, our dinner

36:36.390 --> 36:37.950
will really be too late.

36:38.540 --> 36:39.430
You take the lead.

36:39.430 --> 36:40.580
Tell me what to do.

36:41.920 --> 36:43.730
How about you help me devein the shrimp?

36:43.760 --> 36:45.070
No problem. I can do that.

36:45.710 --> 36:46.620
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

36:48.620 --> 36:49.500
I'll get you something to drink.

36:49.500 --> 36:50.390
No need.

36:50.390 --> 36:51.180
It's okay.

36:57.020 --> 36:58.270
The soup will be ready soon.

36:58.290 --> 36:58.950
Please wait a moment.

37:04.920 --> 37:06.350
Hurry, show it to her.

37:06.350 --> 37:06.710
Look.

37:06.710 --> 37:07.460
Time to eat.

37:07.620 --> 37:08.580
Got it.

37:08.980 --> 37:11.100
He was so chubby when he was little.

37:12.020 --> 37:12.870
It was fine.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.040
How cute.

37:17.310 --> 37:18.150
Look at this one.

37:25.930 --> 37:28.130
Grandpa, why are you showing my photos to Xifan?

37:28.180 --> 37:30.350
You were very cute when you were little.

37:30.350 --> 37:32.100
Much cuter than you are now.

37:32.620 --> 37:33.350
I think so too.

37:35.310 --> 37:36.710
Let's eat. The dinner is ready.

37:36.710 --> 37:37.500
Alright.

37:37.500 --> 37:38.460
Let's eat.

37:38.460 --> 37:39.500
Stop looking. Let's eat.

37:39.500 --> 37:40.270
Okay.

37:40.870 --> 37:41.980
Mr. Shen, Ms. Liu,

37:41.980 --> 37:43.450
today, you should try

37:43.620 --> 37:44.580
Suye's cooking.

37:44.910 --> 37:45.790
Okay.

37:45.790 --> 37:46.660
Xifan.

37:47.060 --> 37:47.790
Thank you.

37:47.810 --> 37:48.460
Please sit down.

37:48.460 --> 37:48.910
Let me do it.

37:48.910 --> 37:49.540
Please, have a seat.

37:49.540 --> 37:50.140
You don't need to do it.

37:50.140 --> 37:51.140
Alright, alright.

37:55.690 --> 37:57.920
It's Mr. Shen's own recipe.

37:57.950 --> 37:58.720
Please try it.

38:00.740 --> 38:01.500
The Chinese medicine is a bit too hot.

38:01.500 --> 38:02.350
Why don't you drink it later?

38:02.350 --> 38:02.970
Let me check.

38:03.350 --> 38:04.060
Oh, it's too hot.

38:04.060 --> 38:05.570
I can't drink it now.

38:05.600 --> 38:07.460
Ms. Liu, are you feeling unwell?

38:07.460 --> 38:08.310
Why are you taking medicinal soup?

38:08.980 --> 38:11.070
He prescribed it for me last time.

38:11.110 --> 38:12.890
He said it would help with my health.

38:15.500 --> 38:16.750
Let me check your pulse.

38:17.220 --> 38:18.410
That would be so great.

38:18.610 --> 38:19.330
Come on.

38:19.430 --> 38:20.580
Do you need something to put under it?

38:21.350 --> 38:23.100
A towel will do.

38:30.890 --> 38:31.810
Look at Grandpa.

38:32.250 --> 38:33.830
He's usually alone at home in the countryside,

38:33.830 --> 38:34.660
and it's been boring.

38:34.660 --> 38:36.430
He's so happy to be here today.

38:37.020 --> 38:39.310
Well, you should come more often in the future.

38:39.510 --> 38:41.910
Of course, as long as you're okay with it.

38:44.820 --> 38:45.900
It's fine. Just leave them to me.

38:55.680 --> 38:57.160
Let me check your tongue coating.

38:59.210 --> 39:00.250
Okay.

39:03.230 --> 39:04.660
Since she started taking

39:04.660 --> 39:06.460
the medicine He prescribed,

39:06.620 --> 39:07.850
there's been quite a big change,

39:08.140 --> 39:09.460
especially in her temperament.

39:09.620 --> 39:11.250
It's improved a lot compared to before.

39:13.060 --> 39:13.910
Don't listen to him.

39:13.910 --> 39:14.910
Actually,

39:14.910 --> 39:17.310
I just felt a bit tight in my chest before.

39:17.310 --> 39:19.580
I felt like I couldn't breathe. Since I started taking the medicine,

39:19.580 --> 39:20.910
it has really improved.

39:22.620 --> 39:23.150
Here.

39:23.390 --> 39:24.470
Let me check this hand.

39:28.100 --> 39:30.190
Since Suye's medicine

39:30.390 --> 39:31.580
has had a good effect,

39:32.350 --> 39:34.180
you should continue taking it for a while.

39:34.270 --> 39:34.870
Okay.

39:38.480 --> 39:39.370
Is everything alright?

39:39.400 --> 39:40.950
Yes. You're fine.

39:43.830 --> 39:45.830
Have you had your regular physical checkup this year?

39:45.950 --> 39:47.390
I actually haven't done it this year.

39:48.580 --> 39:49.620
I forgot.

39:50.660 --> 39:52.140
Physical checkups are quite important.

39:52.580 --> 39:54.270
Only by combining the results of the checkup

39:54.270 --> 39:56.430
with external symptoms

39:56.910 --> 39:59.230
can you fully understand

39:59.290 --> 40:01.080
a person's health status.

40:01.390 --> 40:02.830
So, I suggest you

40:02.950 --> 40:04.230
get one.

40:04.540 --> 40:05.290
Okay.

40:05.500 --> 40:06.690
I'll schedule it for next month.

40:06.750 --> 40:07.460
I'm thinking of

40:07.480 --> 40:08.330
having one next month.

40:09.890 --> 40:12.170
Mr. Shen, let me check your pulse as well.

40:13.170 --> 40:14.560
That would be so great.

40:14.580 --> 40:15.270
Come, come.

40:15.810 --> 40:16.570
Let me.

40:17.140 --> 40:18.580
I'll take off my watch.

40:20.850 --> 40:22.650
I'm doing well.

40:22.680 --> 40:25.070
It's just that sometimes I don't sleep very well.

40:35.120 --> 40:36.680
I've submitted my resignation.

40:36.870 --> 40:39.100
I'll officially leave in a month.

40:43.560 --> 40:49.890
[Submitted Successfully]

41:03.020 --> 41:03.830
I'm back.

41:04.430 --> 41:05.280
What's this?

41:05.880 --> 41:06.530
It's so heavy.

41:07.360 --> 41:09.100
These are things from my office.

41:09.350 --> 41:11.430
I'm planning to move them back little by little,

41:11.430 --> 41:13.500
like ants moving their home.

41:13.580 --> 41:14.980
Can't you just move everything at once?

41:15.010 --> 41:16.090
Why do you have to move them bit by bit?

41:16.370 --> 41:16.920
No.

41:31.910 --> 41:33.060
So much?

41:37.350 --> 41:39.020
Whenever regular customers come,

41:39.020 --> 41:40.910
I spray their favorite scents

41:40.910 --> 41:41.830
on their

41:41.830 --> 41:43.580
welcome cards.

41:44.100 --> 41:46.390
I used to use different perfumes

41:46.390 --> 41:47.690
depending on my mood each day.

41:47.790 --> 41:48.870
I didn't realize how much I've bought

41:48.870 --> 41:50.350
until I started organizing.

41:52.580 --> 41:54.340
This one seems like men's perfume.

41:54.460 --> 41:55.380
Want to give it a try?

41:55.750 --> 41:57.830
No, I don't usually wear perfume.

41:58.840 --> 42:01.240
Alright, then I'll give it away.

42:07.470 --> 42:08.910
Can I have this pen?

42:09.750 --> 42:10.950
What do you need a pen for?

42:11.620 --> 42:13.710
Ballpoint pens are like currency in the hospital.

42:14.750 --> 42:15.950
This one is so noticeable.

42:16.540 --> 42:17.710
I'd like to see

42:17.710 --> 42:20.100
who's been stealing pens from me.
